---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 69
  - Title: Srimad Bhagavatam
    Location: XI iv
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Separation-Sin=Anatomy of the Fallen State
---
As fire appears to have small or great volume, and beginning and end. through
being falsely identified with the burning wood, so does the Atman appear to
take on the attributes of the body by dwelling within it.
